---
import BaseHead from '../components/BaseHead.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
import { SITE_DESCRIPTION, SITE_TITLE } from '../consts';
---

<!doctype html>
<html lang="ko">
	<head>
		<BaseHead title={`About - ${SITE_TITLE}`} description={SITE_DESCRIPTION} />
		<style>
			main {
				max-width: 800px; /* Quieter, slightly narrower than post view for readability */
				margin: 0 auto;
				padding: 3rem 1.5rem;
			}
			.help-title {
				font-family: var(--font-mono);
				font-size: 1.5rem;
				color: var(--green);
				margin-top: 0;
				margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
				display: flex;
				align-items: center;
				gap: 0.5rem;
			}
			.help-prompt {
				color: var(--muted);
				user-select: none;
			}
			
			/* Quiet section styling inspired by manual/help pages */
			.help-section {
				margin-bottom: 2rem;
				display: grid;
				grid-template-columns: 180px 1fr;
				gap: 1.5rem;
			}
			
			.section-name {
				font-family: var(--font-mono);
				font-weight: 700;
				color: var(--yellow);
				font-size: 0.95rem;
				text-transform: uppercase;
				letter-spacing: 0.05em;
				margin: 0;
				padding-top: 0.1rem;
			}
			
			.section-content {
				margin: 0;
				color: var(--text);
				font-size: 1rem;
				line-height: 1.8;
			}
			.section-content p {
				margin: 0 0 1rem 0;
			}
			.section-content p:last-child {
				margin-bottom: 0;
			}
			
			.signature-block {
				margin-top: 4rem;
				border-top: 1px dashed var(--border);
				padding-top: 2rem;
			}
			.signature-text {
				font-size: 0.85rem;
				line-height: 1.6;
				color: #4c566a;
				margin: 0;
			}
			.exit-code {
				font-family: var(--font-mono);
				font-size: 0.8rem;
				color: #4c566a;
				margin-top: 1rem;
			}

			@media (max-width: 640px) {
				.help-section {
					grid-template-columns: 1fr;
					gap: 0.5rem;
					margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
				}
				.section-name {
					border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
					padding-bottom: 0.25rem;
				}
				main {
					padding: 2rem 1rem;
				}
			}
		</style>
	</head>
	<body>
		<Header />
		<main>
			<h1 class="help-title">
				<span class="help-prompt">$</span> joseph --help
			</h1>

			<div class="help-section">
				<h2 class="section-name">NAME</h2>
				<div class="section-content">
					<p>Joseph Kim</p>
				</div>
			</div>

			<div class="help-section">
				<h2 class="section-name">DESCRIPTION</h2>
				<div class="section-content">
					<p>기술, 사업, 문서, 자동화가 서로 꼬이지 않게 정리하는 일을 합니다.</p>
				</div>
			</div>

			<div class="help-section">
				<h2 class="section-name">INTERESTS</h2>
				<div class="section-content">
					<p>AI 워크플로우, 자동화, 문서와 슬라이드, 맥과 윈도우를 다룹니다.</p>
				</div>
			</div>

			<div class="help-section">
				<h2 class="section-name">PREFERENCES</h2>
				<div class="section-content">
					<p>새로운 도구는 좋아하지만, 도구를 관리하느라 일이 늘어나는 건 싫어합니다.</p>
					<p>복잡하고 거창한 방법보다 직관적이고 오래 쓸 수 있는 단순한 방법을 선호합니다.</p>
				</div>
			</div>

			<div class="help-section">
				<h2 class="section-name">NOTES</h2>
				<div class="section-content">
					<p>잘된 일보다 왜 일이 꼬였는지, 어떻게 풀었는지를 더 자주 적습니다.</p>
				</div>
			</div>

			<div class="signature-block">
				<p class="signature-text">돌아는 갑니다.</p>
				<p class="signature-text">계속 쓸지는 모르겠습니다.</p>
				<div class="exit-code">
					// exit code: 0
				</div>
			</div>
		</main>
		<Footer />
	</body>
</html>
